  testing,L2,test execution (exitCode=0),true,"All 7 TCs pass. File system verification and build check confirm all ACs met.\n\nTC-AC1-01: PASS - 0 half-width katakana duplicate directories remain\nTC-AC2-01: PASS - 43 directories renamed from half-width to full-width katakana\nTC-AC3-01: PASS - Old project dirs (Claude-Vision-OCR, Remotion, etc.) all deleted\nTC-AC4-01: PASS - 4 category dirs: bugfix(49), feature(37), workflow-harness(93), investigation(39)\nTC-AC5-01: PASS - 0 loose .md files at root\nTC-AC6-01: PASS - Root contains only bugfix/, feature/, investigation/, workflow-harness/ + docs-workflows-refactoring/\nTC-A","2026-03-24T14:48:22.122Z"
